description:
After all the love you have given their hit single Maafiyan, VYRL Originals brings together the multitalented twins Sukriti-Prakriti and Mellow D for another groovy song - Majnu, starring the handsome sibling duo Abhishek & Siddharth Nigam seen together for the very first time in a music video. This vibrant music video has been directed by Sneha Shetty Kohli who brings out the sizzling chemistry between Sukriti - Prakriti and Abhishek and Siddharth Nigam.
